{
  "stem": "3855.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember it fondly because I was really short and I had to stand on a rather high pedestal to read the scripture.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't recall the chapter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's probably in-- in the [? memento ?] that I have.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I'd like to say it was a family occasion.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's what it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Same for my brother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were no bat mitzvahs in those days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That is a new procedure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so my sister was not involved in that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My father-- there's a little thing I want to tell you which has stuck with me the rest of my life, even though I don't do it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My father used to get us together on Friday and bless us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And even though his Hebrew was very limited, he made it through the [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that has stuck with me all my life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And while I haven't visited a synagogue except on family occasions-- bar mitzvahs or weddings-- I do listen regularly to WQXR.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when it comes to the blessings, I really-- it rips open all this memory, and it really means something to me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that is the tradition that stays with me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I haven't continued that with my children for other reasons.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But when you're born a Jew, you're a Jew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Doesn't matter whether you are religious, whether you believe in every little-- there is no dot on the i, but whether you believe in every i, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I believe it's something that's evolved over thousands of years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I'm not a biologist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I don't know everything in your genes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But I'm almost tempted to say it is.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the events that you go through sometimes minimize it and sometimes accentuate it, but the level stays there.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
